l of eye pouch\nes and jowls can be a great help.\nA man must realize that his\nshort haircut reveals the small\nfacelift scars that a woman\u2019s\nhair and make-up cover. The\nscars often are a greater cause\nof embarrassment than the\nwrinkles.\nThe operation causing the most\ncomment these days is the breast\noperation which makes small\nbreasts larger, or reduces the\nsize of overlarge breasts. The\nwomen with overlarge breasts\nsuffer much physical discomfort.\nIn England over-large breasts\nare recognized as a medical prob\nlem and surgery to reduce their\nsize now falls within the realm\nof socialized medicine.\nThe operation to enlarge the\nsize of breats is still met with\nmuch controversy. We think that\nthis operation is a bit of hog\nwash and should not be perform\nied.\nGADSDEN COUNTY TIMES, QUINCY, FLORIDA, THURSDAY, JUNE 19, 1958\nIT COULD BE YOU\nMANNING TAYLOR CHEVROLET CO.\nIS DETERMINED TO GIVE THIS CAR TO SOMEONE ABSOLUTELY FREE! YOU DON'T HAVE\nTO BUY YOU DON'T EVEN HAVE TO LOOK AT ANYTHING\nBUT DO BE SUU TO\nREGISTER\n1951 BUICK McWWjFS SBpSi DRAWING\nSTATION WAGON WILL BE HELD\nFREE _ SATURDAY,\nHere's Utility, Beauty and JUNE 28th\nEconomy all Wrapped Up MRS\nIn A Single Unit. K 6:00 P.M.\nIt's Clean It's Extra w X i\n11m\nYOU MUST BE\nPRESENT TO WIN i\nll3\n$1695 JUNE IS THE MONTH 51595\n1956 BUICK TO BUY! 1956 BUICK\nCentury, 2-Dr. Hardtop M WAR I I Special, 4-Door, R4H, Air\nLoaded. 300 HP. A real buy OK USED Conditioned. Family Spedal\nWE WILL SAVE YOU MONEY ON ANY\neft n e CAR YOU SELECT LOW GMAC FINANCE e >ft\n995 PLAN -NO PAYMENT FOR 45 DAYS $095 i\n1956 CHEVROLET THE PROOF 1954 CHEVROLET j\nW Ton Pickup, truck, R&H H A q g j Ml 4-Door, 6 Cyl. Heater, New\nl5 vN IHE Paint. A Honey\n7^7 PRICE TAG\n1958 CHEVROLET DID YOU KNOW j 5,795\nYOU CAN BUY THIS GAS-SAVING, LOW OPERATING COST IQW rurVPAT FT\nStation Wagon, V-8, Auto. '5B CHEVROLET DELRAY AWf UHLfHULDI\nTrans., R&H, WW Tires FOR ONLY 4-Door,'2lo', Heater, 2-tone,\nOnly 1200 Miles. 